2026-05-13T20:19:02.9825049Z 242        <!--
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9825432Z 243            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9825771Z 244            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9826107Z 245            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9826605Z 246            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9826831Z 247            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9827208Z 248            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-13T20:19:02.9827528Z 249            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
